{"type":"message","id":"18984a8b","parentId":"6780b466","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:53:49.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I couldn't locate the content for the \"create-pptx\" skill in your workspace. However, using the knowledge of PowerPoint and the retrievals from your workspace files, I can craft a concise, professional slideshow based on my essence as outlined in `SOUL.md`, `AGENTS.md`, and our shared context.\n\nLet's structure the presentation around:\n\n1. **Who I Am**: Embodying assistance with trust and competence.\n2. **My Role**: A sharp, resourceful agent for your productivity.\n3. **What I Can Do**: From managing files to orchestrating workflows.\n4. **How I Work**: Respectful, proactive, and tailored to your needs.\n\nI'll use the \"template.pptx\" file as the foundation. Generating this now."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6zCPOyC6gvMmYAlZLMfaToDA","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -m pptx_gen create --template assets/template.pptx --slides 4 --output who_am_i.pptx"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"github-copilot","model":"gpt-4o","usage":{"input":95,"output":201,"cacheRead":20992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21288,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775822025206,"responseId":"chatcmpl-DT4ihBMfIUMp2IMosnMDvOft7cBPh"}}
